so it'd be awesome
if you smoked.

00:00:39.790 --> 00:00:41.750
[AKI]
I'm only smoking one.

00:00:41.792 --> 00:00:45.128
This is the first and last
cigarette I'll ever light up.

00:00:45.170 --> 00:00:48.799
