smoking's out for you, duh!

00:00:59.476 --> 00:01:01.019
[sighs]

00:01:03.855 --> 00:01:05.566
Give it here.

00:01:07.859 --> 00:01:09.486
I'll just hafta hang onto this.

00:01:09.528 --> 00:01:11.780
