00:01:13.865 --> 00:01:15.617
I'll return it one day, though.

00:01:15.659 --> 00:01:17.744
As soon as you're
a full-fledged grownup

00:01:17.786 --> 00:01:19.496
ready for a good addiction.

00:01:19.538 --> 00:01:26.503
[AKI panting]

00:02:33.570 --> 00:02:36.156
[AKI] The Ghost Devil
doesn't have eyes.

00:02:36.198 --> 00:02:38.617
It uses fear to see.

00:02:38.659 --> 00:02:40.535
Thanks for explaining
that, Himeno.

00:02:40.577 --> 00:02:42.371
[gasps]

00:02:58.929 --> 00:03:00.681
[AKI]
Himeno.

00:03:02.432 --> 00:03:04.726
[AKI]
I'll be with you soon.

00:03:08.271 --> 00:03:09.564
[AKI grunts]

00:05:19.903 --> 00:05:20.737
Snake--!

00:05:20.779 --> 00:05:21.655
