[DENJI]
Hm?

00:06:08.451 --> 00:06:11.580
Ew, gross!

00:06:11.621 --> 00:06:14.124
Huh? If it's meat, I eat.

00:06:14.165 --> 00:06:16.543
Bovine, porcine, human--
it matters not!

00:06:16.585 --> 00:06:18.712
It sure as hell does!

00:06:20.213 --> 00:06:21.381
[DENJI]
You better not try to munch on

00:06:21.423 --> 00:06:23.258
that Samurai Sword dude.

00:06:23.300 --> 00:06:26.553
Our mission is to capture him.

00:06:26.595 --> 00:06:27.971
Got it?

00:06:38.231 --> 00:06:40.066
They haven't seen we're here.

00:06:40.108 --> 00:06:42.736
Don't make any loud noises.

00:06:44.279 --> 00:06:46.573
[POWER] You stand in
the presence of Power!

00:06:46.615 --> 00:06:47.449
Huh?!

00:06:47.490 --> 00:06:50.118
We'll defeat them
with ease. 'Tis a battle!

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:52.162
[ZOMBIES groan]

00:06:52.203 --> 00:06:54.539
Denji. Take heart and follow me.

00:06:54.581 --> 00:06:57.000
My back is yours to protect!

00:06:57.042 --> 00:07:01.588
[POWER grunts]

00:07:01.630 --> 00:07:03.632
Ha! What say you now?

00:07:03.673 --> 00:07:05.050
I have not fled!

00:07:05.091 --> 00:07:08.011
I am proud and beautiful!

00:07:09.471 --> 00:07:12.057
[POWER]
A worthy adversary appears.

00:07:12.098 --> 00:07:13.600
Denji. Observe.

00:07:13.642 --> 00:07:15.018
Bear witness to this day!

00:07:15.060 --> 00:07:18.688
And tell the tale of Power,
the greatest of them all!

00:07:18.730 --> 00:07:21.524
[POWER cackling]

00:07:29.741 --> 00:07:33.578
[yawns]

00:07:45.715 --> 00:07:47.926
Been lookin' for you, Sideburns.

00:07:47.968 --> 00:07:49.469
Whoa, whoa, hold on a sec.

00:07:49.511 --> 00:07:51.554
Let's you and I have a chat.

00:07:51.596 --> 00:07:52.889
[DENJI]
Hm?

00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:57.435
Based on how you
decide to play it,

00:07:57.477 --> 00:08:00.397
we're willin' to give up
'n' turn ourselves in.

00:08:00.438 --> 00:08:01.481
We just want a little closure

00:08:01.523 --> 00:08:04.359
to take summa the sting
outta this anger.

00:08:08.154 --> 00:08:10.407
[SAMURAI SWORD]
Denji, it's no secret you killed

00:08:10.448 --> 00:08:12.909
their friends and my granddad.

00:08:12.951 --> 00:08:15.787
Why not atone and
right your wrongs?

00:08:15.829 --> 00:08:18.373
I mean, somebody else
killed 'em first.

00:08:18.415 --> 00:08:20.291
Those guys were zombified, dude.

00:08:20.333 --> 00:08:21.835
Don't you fucking lie!

00:08:21.876 --> 00:08:25.088
Little shits like you
are always blowin' smoke!

00:08:26.339 --> 00:08:27.841
All right, fine.

00:08:27.882 --> 00:08:31.052
Say that whole zombie scenario
was the hard truth.

00:08:31.094 --> 00:08:34.556
