one point. And you killed 'em.

00:08:34.597 --> 00:08:36.808
Don't you feel the slightest
shred of remorse?

00:08:36.850 --> 00:08:39.144
Nah, I'm good.

00:08:39.185 --> 00:08:40.854
[SAMURAI SWORD chuckles]

00:08:40.895 --> 00:08:43.273
Y'know, I've been put through
the wringer, too.

00:08:43.314 --> 00:08:47.902
Sawatari replaced my heart
with the Katana Devil somehow.

00:08:47.944 --> 00:08:49.821
But even I have trouble
sleepin' on nights

00:08:49.863 --> 00:08:51.281
when I've slipped up
and sent zombies

00:08:51.322 --> 00:08:54.034
on another trip
to the afterlife.

00:08:54.909 --> 00:08:56.745
I ain't completely heartless.

00:08:56.786 --> 00:08:59.289
But I guess that just
makes one of us, huh?

00:08:59.330 --> 00:09:02.709
If you got any kind of
conscience left in there,

00:09:02.751 --> 00:09:06.004
you should do the world
a favor and let us kill you.

00:09:11.760 --> 00:09:13.094
No thanks.

00:09:14.763 --> 00:09:16.973
Then that's that.

00:09:17.015 --> 00:09:19.100
