scrawny ass even more!

00:09:19.142 --> 00:09:22.187
I'd like to see you try!
Heh, heh!

00:09:28.818 --> 00:09:29.611
[DENJI]
Heh heh!

00:09:29.652 --> 00:09:30.528
What the--?

00:09:30.570 --> 00:09:32.280
[DENJI] Thought my
scrawny ass was grass.

00:09:32.322 --> 00:09:35.325
What happened, huh? I'm waiting!

00:09:38.703 --> 00:09:43.500
[DENJI yells]

00:09:43.541 --> 00:09:45.085
[SAMURAI SWORD]
Die!

00:09:47.170 --> 00:09:49.172
[SAMURAI SWORD grunts]

00:09:50.882 --> 00:09:57.097
[SAMURAI SWORD grunting]

00:10:02.185 --> 00:10:04.020
[DENJI grunts]

00:10:09.859 --> 00:10:12.529
[DENJI gasps]

00:10:12.570 --> 00:10:14.989
[SAMURAI SWORD grunts]

00:10:18.743 --> 00:10:21.663
[DENJI groans]

