all day for it.

00:10:59.617 --> 00:11:02.579
Cocky for someone who
has no hope of winning.

00:11:02.620 --> 00:11:05.456
What? You really think
you've got me beat already?

00:11:05.498 --> 00:11:07.417
If I got a pulse,
I got a chance!

00:11:07.458 --> 00:11:09.127
