00:11:33.234 --> 00:11:34.485
[SAMURAI SWORD grunts]

00:11:34.527 --> 00:11:37.155
[PASSENGERS gasp]

00:11:38.531 --> 00:11:39.616
[CONDUCTOR A]
Due to an incident...

00:11:39.657 --> 00:11:42.660
[DENJI]
