00:11:45.538 --> 00:11:48.124
[DENJI gasps]

00:11:48.166 --> 00:11:51.794
[SAMURAI SWORD grunts]

00:11:51.836 --> 00:11:53.463
[CONDUCTOR A] Please evacuate
in an orderly fashion

00:11:53.504 --> 00:11:54.923
