00:12:30.625 --> 00:12:35.129
Can't fight without your arms,
so how 'bout it, Denji?

00:12:36.381 --> 00:12:38.591
[SAMURAI SWORD] Why not
use your last few breaths

00:12:38.633 --> 00:12:41.594
to apologize for
killin' Granddad?

00:12:48.101 --> 00:12:51.104
Who says I can't still fight?

00:12:53.606 --> 00:12:56.985
The chainsaw on my head
is all I need to end this!

00:12:57.026 --> 00:12:58.528
Moron!

00:13:09.080 --> 00:13:11.958
[SAMURAI SWORD] Didn't my
granddad ever teach you

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:14.502
to know when to quit?

00:13:15.795 --> 00:13:21.467
Grovel for his mercy and I'll
put you outta your misery.

00:13:26.472 --> 00:13:29.934
[DENJI] You put the
"dick" in predictable

00:13:29.976 --> 00:13:34.647
and went for my head
like a dipshit!

00:13:34.689 --> 00:13:36.107
Huh?

00:13:39.986 --> 00:13:43.614
Didn't that rotten
old geezer ever teach ya?

00:13:43.656 --> 00:13:44.657
Beasts should know better

00:13:44.699 --> 00:13:46.868
than to trust what
a hunter says!

00:13:46.909 --> 00:13:50.538
Shoulda gone for
the legs, suckah!

00:13:50.580 --> 00:13:55.168
[SAMURAI SWORD groaning]

00:14:21.944 --> 00:14:24.739
[footsteps]

00:14:24.781 --> 00:14:27.241
[DENJI]
Well, look who's awake.

00:14:29.243 --> 00:14:30.912
We really are alike.

00:14:30.953 --> 00:14:33.164
Who would've thunk it, huh?

00:14:33.206 --> 00:14:35.124
