robbed the world

00:15:03.361 --> 00:15:05.738
of one serious hottie.

00:15:05.780 --> 00:15:07.657
And now you're gonna
live out your life in jail

00:15:07.698 --> 00:15:10.576
without being sorry for it?

00:15:10.618 --> 00:15:13.704
That won't leave
a good taste in my mouth.

00:15:13.746 --> 00:15:16.374
You talk like you can
do something about it,

00:15:16.416 --> 00:15:19.043
but you're just
Public Safety's mutt!

00:15:23.005 --> 00:15:27.343
[DENJI gasps]
How's about a 'lil contest?

00:15:27.385 --> 00:15:29.512
Huh?

00:15:29.554 --> 00:15:30.763
[AKI]
Contest?

00:15:30.805 --> 00:15:34.225
Huh? Hey, perfect timing!

00:15:36.018 --> 00:15:37.812
Hayakawa, Squad Four.

00:15:37.854 --> 00:15:39.856
