on the train tracks,

00:15:39.897 --> 00:15:41.774
the ones in front of
the clock tower.

00:15:41.816 --> 00:15:43.526
Send backup.

00:15:43.568 --> 00:15:45.820
[DENJI] Wanna get in
on this, too, Hayakawa?

00:15:45.862 --> 00:15:48.156
I guarantee it'll be the tits!

00:15:48.197 --> 00:15:50.616
What the hell
are you talking about?

00:15:52.994 --> 00:15:54.871
[DENJI]
I figured since he shot Himeno,

00:15:54.912 --> 00:15:56.664
we should get to
take shots at him.

00:15:56.706 --> 00:15:58.791
It's only fair, yeah?

00:16:00.835 --> 00:16:03.087
Except it'll be like a contest!

00:16:03.129 --> 00:16:06.466
We'll take turns giving him
the hardest nut shots we can,

00:16:06.507 --> 00:16:08.342
