00:16:24.108 --> 00:16:26.068
[AKI]
Our job is to catch this guy,

00:16:26.110 --> 00:16:28.321
and we're still on a mission.

00:16:28.362 --> 00:16:31.949
We shouldn't torture him to
make ourselves feel better.

00:16:31.991 --> 00:16:34.076
Not like it'll bring her back.

00:16:34.118 --> 00:16:36.746
I doubt she would even approve.

00:16:37.997 --> 00:16:40.208
Huh. Oh, yeah?

00:17:04.649 --> 00:17:05.942
[AKI]
So.

00:17:07.276 --> 00:17:09.237
