00:17:09.278 --> 00:17:14.075
Heh. I thought his family jewels
would make for a nice prize!

00:17:14.116 --> 00:17:15.701
[AKI chuckles]

00:17:15.743 --> 00:17:17.995
[SAMURAI SWORD] Wait. You--
You aren't really gonna do it,

00:17:18.037 --> 00:17:20.915
are you? Guys, come on--!

00:17:35.721 --> 00:17:38.224
[sighs]

00:17:38.266 --> 00:17:41.310
[yawns]

00:17:52.154 --> 00:17:53.864
[screams]

00:17:53.906 --> 00:17:56.909
[DENJI]
Yeah!

00:17:56.951 --> 00:18:00.788
[AKI] Himeno. Can you
hear this up in heaven?

00:18:00.830 --> 00:18:01.789
[AKI grunts]

00:18:01.831 --> 00:18:04.959
[screams]

00:18:05.001 --> 00:18:09.630
[AKI]
