with the Gun Devil

00:18:24.270 --> 00:18:26.939
and distributed firearms
to the yakuza,

00:18:26.981 --> 00:18:29.567
but the payment she
demanded wasn't monetary.

00:18:29.609 --> 00:18:31.485
