before you explained

00:18:36.240 --> 00:18:39.243
why that girl was after
the Chainsaw Devil's heart.

00:18:39.285 --> 00:18:42.330
Unfortunately, we lost
our chance to ask.

00:18:42.371 --> 00:18:43.998
[gasps]

00:18:45.458 --> 00:18:48.002
[screams]

00:18:48.044 --> 00:18:49.462
[EXECUTIVE B]
Suicide, huh?

00:18:49.503 --> 00:18:51.380
